{"tid":2167401,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"通識書可唔可以將「審查通識書」呢件事寫入去？","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:38:09.000Z","uid":96708,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8da1cf84444717219338416f580a169f5d0c95da","tid":2167401,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">2020年八月，教育局要求出版商在通識課本中刪減多項內容，包括刪走「三權分立」定義、把「本土意識」與「民主派」字眼，分別改為「本地意識」及「非建制派」，修訂多幅諷刺政府的漫畫等，而有關2014年香港市民反對831人大決定所引發的「雨傘運動」的資料更被全數刪去，理由是「社會事件過時」。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />通識考考你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請細閱以上內容後，回答以下問題並詳述你的理據：<br />\n<br />\n1) 你認為教育局的決定合理嗎？為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n2) 考慮2019至2020香港的社會狀況，你認為教育局的要求是政治審查的一種嗎？<br />\n<br />\n3) 你認為審查通識科會令學生減少接觸相關事件嗎？"},{"pid":"b6ac069625395fd846a0ca471bab2d3c58244bfa","tid":2167401,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f901f182cfb36f78260603d23d24fe73f3f4c9e9","tid":2167401,"uid":650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1a2866236b09a5641c0d52b906297401b7dac1","tid":2167401,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186f7f2b86f496c95443de1ffe2fe981c07e917a","tid":2167401,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a32d360f6bbf65946b50e51ef85fd6e0dd60c61","tid":2167401,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648e56486a23d737dfd9e10967c13a20a76a9f40","tid":2167401,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}